title: Looking for a Plat+ Support to finish off the main Roster for Besieged By Fate!
body:
Hello everyone, Besieged By Fate is currently looking for a Plat+ Support just to finish out it's main Roster

This is the Current Schedule for the Team we are hoping to find someone who can work with this!
Monday - Flex
Tuesday - Flex or Scrim
Wednesday - Scrim or Tournament

if you are interested please don't hesitate in filling out this form thanks!
